  "body": "As has been pointed out thanx to @ibrkhalil, app layout doesn't fit well after changing device' screen zoom/font style settings. This results in poor user experience for those users who are using their device with changed screen zoom/font size setting due to sight issues. \r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n1. Change screen zoom/font size settings: set everything to max value for better result observing\r\n2. Open Status app\r\n3. Go through different screen\r\n4. Pay attention at layout\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** layout looks pretty unusable broken, some elements (like bottom tabs) are unvisible. \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/208696747-e3f32812-3a1a-4106-8402-0e1a4179affe.mp4\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
