    "body": "> We can scale text to match what's selected in settings like [here](https://spin.atomicobject.com/2021/11/12/3-ways-scale-react-native-app/#:~:text=The%20fontScale%20can%20range%20from,font%20scale%20of%20the%20device.)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nOr we can lock the text size and don't allow it to scale in respect to accessibility settings If we don't support scaling of UI in our app.\r\n\r\nWe just need to set [`allowFontScaling`](https://reactnative.dev/docs/text#allowfontscaling) props to `false` on text components.\r\n",
